<html>
    <head>
        <title>MangoDude</title>
        <meta charset="UTF-8" />
        <meta
            name="viewport"
            content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1, shrink-to-fit=no"
        />
        <link
            rel="stylesheet"
            href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@4.5.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css"
            integrity="sha384-TX8t27EcRE3e/ihU7zmQxVncDAy5uIKz4rEkgIXeMed4M0jlfIDPvg6uqKI2xXr2"
            crossorigin="anonymous"
        />
        <link rel="stylesheet" href="style.css" />
    </head>
    <body class="bg-dark text-light">
        <div class="fixed-top container">
            <div class="float-right text-monospace">
                <a href="#account" class="btn btn-link">Account</a>
                <a href="#code" class="btn btn-link">Code</a>
                <a href="#api" class="btn btn-link">API</a>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="container">
            <div class="jumbotron bg-dark">
                <h1 class="text-center">MangoDude</h1>
                <hr class="my-4" />
                <p class="lead">A small game project.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="container rounded border border-primary text-light p-3">
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-md-6" id="account">
                    <h3>&#129389; Manage your account</h3>
                    <p>
                        You can manage your MangoDude account on this website.
                    </p>
                    <p>
                        Logging in gives you the oppurtunity to change your
                        password. You <b>cannot</b> change your username though.
                        You just can't.
                    </p>
                    <p>
                        In order to manage your account, you have to log in. You
                        cannot sign up through the website.
                    </p>
                    <a href="/login" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg">Log In</a>
                </div>

                <div class="col-md-6" id="code">
                    <h3>&#129389; Code</h3>
                    <p>
                        The code of this project (both front-end and back-end)
                        is available on GitHub. Check them out now!
                    </p>
                    <ul class="list-unstyled">
                        <li>
                            <a
                                href="https://github.com/geniusjam/mangodude"
                                class="text-light"
                            >
                                Front-end Repo
                            </a>
                        </li>
                        <li>
                            <a
                                href="https://github.com/geniusjam/mangodude-backend"
                                class="text-light"
                            >
                                Back-end Repo
                            </a>
                        </li>
                        <li class="mt-3">
                            <a
                                href="https://github.com/geniusjam"
                                class="text-light"
                            >
                                GitHub profile of the author
                            </a>
                        </li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="row" id="api">
                <div class="col-md-6">
                    <h3>&#129389; API</h3>
                    <p>
                        No documentation for now. There are plans for the
                        future.
                        <i
                            >Maybe you can figure the API out from the code?
                            Check the backend code out.</i
                        >
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </body>
</html>
